 Challenge: “Geometry Showcase”
📌 Goal:
Create a 3D scene that includes all the core geometries provided by Three.js.

🧱 Objects Included:
BoxGeometry (Cube)

SphereGeometry

CapsuleGeometry

CylinderGeometry

TorusGeometry

TorusKnotGeometry

ConeGeometry

RingGeometry

PlaneGeometry

🛠️ Features Implemented:
Proper scene, camera, and renderer setup

OrbitControls for interactive viewing 🌀

DirectionalLight + AmbientLight for nice lighting 🎇

Responsive canvas rendering

Clean layout with well-spaced objects

💡 Skill Focus:
Basic geometry usage

Scene setup best practices

Lighting fundamentals

Intro to camera controls

Learning object positioning in 3D space

